  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in about the third day after this little war that we had to do with the-- to the Red Army, I had to report, because I already knew, because there were all kinds of wandering people, people around.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the-- the soldiers, patrols, if they caught you, you had to be-- you had to be on safe ground to do what you are.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I inquired and I got information that such and such a place only [INAUDIBLE] away from my safe house, there is a district Soviet command.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a major was there, and with Therese, the daughter of the Schandl family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She spoke, since she spoke Russian, she spoke German, she spoke English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she interpreted to me in English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so when I introduced myself, you see, in English, she translated that in-- in Russian-- in to-- to-- to the major.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I was checked out, and I told them my-- my-- my code-- code number, ME6.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in-- in-- in five days' time, they checked it out from-- from-- from Debrecen, because that was the allied military-- military mission already.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In five days' time, was checked out, and they put me in a-- and they let me go home to the Schandls for-- for-- for one day and come back, and then I never saw-- saw them again.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they keep me for a couple days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They even took me over to the Transdanubia to see the battlefield, the German and the Soviet battlefield.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- then-- then they took me-- took me out to Debrecen, to the what you call.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there-- from there, well, a lot of things has happened in-- in-- in a few days.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
